# cli-ux self-hosting intent spec

## Changes

- Added `WorkflowSmokeResult` and `SelfHostedWorkflowSmokePasses` to `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent`.
- Added `BinaryProvenanceResult` and `BinaryProvenanceVisible` to `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent`.
- Added `WorkflowBinaryUse`, `WorkflowSmokeDoesNotDependOnParentBinary`, and `SelfHostSmokeUsesCurrentWorkspaceBinary` to `products/cli-ux/intents/self-hosting-invariants.intent`.

## Validation Plan

Run `intent-validate path=products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent format=text` and `intent-validate path=products/cli-ux/intents/invariants.intent format=text`, then run the full product directory.

## Checklist

- [x] Acceptance intents added
- [x] Invariant safety added
- [x] No time/performance constraint placed in intent
